title: (x) Need help identifying Font / Loud comic style - Zoinks [Eric H}
content:
I picked a new client for an apparel account and the old vendor will not release the name of font they used on a few items. Can anyone help identify the attached font? Thanks!!

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20100219213740im_/http:/typophile.com/files/Indiana%20blizzard%20font_4854.jpg)
author: indianablizzard

comments.content: This goes under a few names. [Zoinks](http://web.archive.org/web/20100219213740/http:/new.myfonts.com/fonts/comicraft/zoinks/) is one of them.
